ZHAOKE OPHTHALMOLOGY BRANDING & WEBSITE PROPOSAL

Comprehensive Digital Strategy for ZKO
Theme: “Clarity Through Innovation in Ophthalmology”

Executive Summary
Positioning ZKO as a trusted, visionary leader in ophthalmic therapeutics, emphasizing innovation, clinical credibility, and transparency as a listed company.

1. Core Concept

Theme: “Clarity Through Innovation in Ophthalmology.”

Brand Personality:

Scientific Precision — ophthalmology R&D credibility

Visionary Leadership — pioneering sight-restoring therapies

Transparent & Trusted — global standards and regulatory compliance

Human Impact — vision as the essence of quality of life

2. Visual & UI/UX Design Language
Element	Design Choice	Why
Color Palette	Sky blue, turquoise, and light silver gradients	Evokes vision, clarity, and medical precision
Typography	Modern sans-serif (e.g., Inter, Source Sans Pro)	Elegant, legible, trustworthy
Imagery	Eye close-ups, light beams, optical lenses, lab work	Reinforces ophthalmology identity
Layout	Airy, modular grid	Clean readability, professional trust
Motion	Smooth focus-blur transitions	Mimics vision clarity metaphor
Tone	Calm, intelligent, clinical	Appeals to investors, clinicians, patients
3. Ideal Site Architecture & Content

Homepage

Hero Tagline:

“Innovating Vision. Improving Lives.”

Animated background: iris-to-molecule morphing

Buttons: “Explore Pipeline” / “Investor Center”

Sections:

Integrated Ophthalmic Platform

Pipeline Overview

Manufacturing Excellence (Nansha Facility)

Global Partnerships

Latest News

About Us

History (Founded 2017, HKEX-listed)

Mission, Vision, and Values

Leadership section

Timeline: “From R&D roots to market readiness”

R&D / Technology

Front- & back-of-eye therapeutic focus

Interactive visual flow: Discovery → Clinical → Commercialization

Highlight major indications: DED, Myopia, wAMD, DME, Glaucoma

Pipeline

Phase tracker cards

Candidate	Indication	Phase	Partner
CsA Gel	Dry Eye	Phase III	In-house
NVK-002	Myopia	Phase III	Vyluma
PAN-90806	wAMD	Phase II	PanOptica

Manufacturing

GMP facility spotlight (7,600 m² in Nansha)

3D visual or video walkthrough

Global quality standards (NMPA, EU, FDA alignment)

Partners

Logos and brief collab stories (Visus, Vyluma, Fareva)

Investor Relations

HKEX disclosure feed, PDF downloads, and financial highlights

News & Insights

Press releases, conference updates, medical publications

Contact

Hong Kong HQ and Guangzhou addresses

Interactive map and WeChat QR

4. Functional Features

Dual language: English / 中文

Responsive across devices

SEO optimized for “ophthalmic therapeutics China”, “eye drug development”, etc.

Secure HTTPS + ICP compliant hosting

CMS backend (Sanity, Strapi, or WordPress Headless)

5. Optional Enhancements

Virtual tour of Nansha facility

Download center for regulatory filings and brochures

Investor portal with real-time financial data

Careers portal with dynamic listings

6. Tagline & Slogan Ideas

“Science That Refocuses Sight.”

“From Vision Research to Patient Reality.”

“Precision Ophthalmology, Powered by Innovation.”

“Shaping the Future of Eye Health.”

7. Design Inspiration

Blend corporate biotech elegance (like Roche / Alcon)
with modern vision-care innovation (like Johnson & Johnson Vision or Aerie Pharmaceuticals).
